    "89e7dd7e-57b3-4d96-8976-0028770ff1df": {
      "settings": {
        "background_color": "#e2e2db",
        "custom_background_color": true,
        "heading": "<p><strong>#3 Simple Modern products can be purchased all over the United States.</strong></p>",
        "richtext": "<p>You may have seen Simple Modern products online on Amazon or simplemodern.com. Or perhaps you’ve seen our products on shelves at your local Target, Walmart, or Sam’s Club. Or all of the above!</p><p>Over the last eight years, Simple Modern has established itself as a leading omnichannel drinkware company and has grown into a category leader for retail partners Amazon, Target, Walmart, and Sam’s Club. Simplemodern.com is also the one-stop-shop for all things Simple Modern and features our most extensive product offerings.</p>"
      },
      "type": "simple-text"
    },
