    "fbdb32a5-c8a6-4f7b-9c09-ef0612908129": {
      "settings": {
        "background_color": "#e2e2db",
        "custom_background_color": true,
        "heading": "<p>#1 Simple Modern was founded in Oklahoma in 2015.</p>",
        "richtext": "<p>You may have never been to Oklahoma, but this great state is the birthplace of Simple Modern. Simple Modern was co-founded in 2015 by Mike Beckham, Bryan Porter, and Micah Ames—three friends and graduates from the University of Oklahoma—who wanted to start a company together. Eight years later, our company is still proudly headquartered in the Oklahoma City<br/>metroplex.</p>"
